room_title: Escape room "Back to the 90's" by Great Room Escape in Columbus
review: We went for our anniversary and joined another couple for the 90s throwback. It was both of our first times and we had so much fun! If you live/visit the area I would recommend it!!

room_title: Escape room "Back to the 90's" by Great Room Escape in Columbus
review: It was our first time at an escape room and it was a great experience. We did the Back to the 90s room which was challenging. Thank you Jasmine for the assistance and as our guide!

room_title: Escape room "Back to the 90's" by Great Room Escape in Columbus
review: We went to the Chamber Escape room for my husband's birthday. Casie was very helpful to get all signed in and our game master was fabulous. We did the 90's experience. It was three rooms and much more difficult than I first thought it would be, but we conquered it before the 60-minute time limit was up! Would absolutely recommend this to anyone looking for a fun group date or evening out! Loved it!
